The '''Square of Hierarchy''' was a location on [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]] after its [[Terraforming/Legends|vongforming]] into Yuuzhan'tar, on the former [[Calocour Heights]]. During the [[Battle of Yuuzhan'tar]], [[Nom Anor]] resumed his guise of [[Nom Anor|Yu'shaa]] and defected over to the side of the [[Shamed Ones]] at the Square. The Garrison of [[Warrior caste|Warriors]] from [[Shimrra's Citadel]] tried to herd them to the [[Place of Bones]] from the Square, but [[Jedi Knight/Legends|Jedi Knights]] and troops from the [[Galactic Federation of Free Alliances|Galactic Alliance]] came to the aid of the heretics.

